":[{\"label\":\"check-replays\",\"detail\":\"Review recent degraded replays\"},{\"label\":\"run-regression\",\"detail\":\"Run bound regression set\"},{\"label\":\"bind-gray\",\"detail\":\"Apply gray config if needed\"}]},\"maxRunAgeHours\":24},\"realtime\":{\"gatewayHealth\":{\"status\":\"UP\",\"enabled\":true,\"gatewayMode\":\"internal\",\"providerSummary\":{\"providerCount\":3,\"providers\":{\"event\":{\"implemented\":false,\"entityType\":\"event\",\"reason\":\"provider_not_implemented\"},\"product\":{\"implemented\":true,\"entityType\":\"product\",\"orchestratorEnabled\":true},\"store\":{\"implemented\":false,\"entityType\":\"store\",\"reason\":\"provider_not_implemented\"}}},\"productProviderReady\":true,\"storeProviderReady\":false,\"eventProviderReady\":false},\"status\":{\"enabled\":true,\"gatewayEnabled\":false,\"mockGatewayEnabled\":false,\"cacheSize\":0,\"cacheTtlSeconds\":15,\"maxCandidates\":5,\"metrics\":{\"totalRequests\":9,\"cacheHitCount\":0,\"gatewayRequestCount\":0,\"gatewaySuccessCount\":0,\"gatewayFailureCount\":0,\"fallbackResponseCount\":0,\"rateLimitedCount\":1},\"circuit\":{\"state\":\"CLOSED\",\"remainingOpenMs\":0,\"failureThreshold\":3,\"openSeconds\":30,\"consecutiveFailures\":0,\"lastFailureReason\":null,\"lastFailureAt\":1775969735218,\"lastSuccessAt\":0}},\"mode\":\"fallback_only\",\"launchPathReady\":true},\"rollbackCandidates\":[{\"index\":\"\",\"exists\":false,\"documentCount\":0,\"error\":\"读取 ES alias 失败: product_search_read\"}],\"recommendedActions\":[\"Sync baseline unavailable: 读取 ES alias 失败: product_search_read\",\"Latest regression run is stale.\",\"Prepare at least one usable rollback candidate index.\"]},\"checklist\":[{\"id\":\"sync-baseline-clean\",\"label\":\"Sync baseline clean\",\"ready\":false,\"severity\":\"warning\",\"detail\":\"W12 baseline report has no open mismatches or failed tasks.\",\"action\":\"Run sync repair strategy and clear failed/dead-letter tasks.\"},{\"id\":\"product-index-valid\",\"label\":\"Product index validated\",\"ready\":false,\"severity\":\"warning\",\"detail\":\"Read/write aliases and snapshot reconciliation stay consistent.\",\"action\":\"Validate aliases and rebuild or rollback the product index.\"},{\"id\":\"sync-task-queue-clean\",\"label\":\"Sync task queue clean\",\"ready\":false,\"severity\":\"warning\",\"detail\":\"No failed or dead-letter sync tasks remain.\",\"action\":\"Retry or repair failed sync tasks before launch.\"},{\"id\":\"governance-preflight-ready\",\"label\":\"Governance preflight ready\",\"ready\":false,\"severity\":\"warning\",\"detail\":\"Regression freshness, pass rate, and degraded rate all pass launch thresholds.\",\"action\":\"Run the bound regression set again and fix failed cases.\"},{\"id\":\"realtime-service-ready\",\"label\":\"Realtime service ready\",\"ready\":true,\"severity\":\"info\",\"detail\":\"Realtime service is enabled and the circuit is closed.\",\"action\":\"No action needed.\"},{\"id\":\"realtime-live-gateway\",\"label\":\"Realtime launch path ready\",\"ready\":true,\"severity\":\"info\",\"detail\":\"A usable internal or live realtime gateway is configured for launch.\",\"action\":\"No action needed.\"},{\"id\":\"rollback-candidate-ready\",\"label\":\"Rollback candidate ready\",\"ready\":false,\"severity\":\"warning\",\"detail\":\"At least one usable rollback target index exists.\",\"action\":\"Prepare and validate a rollback candidate index.\"},{\"id\":\"overall-ready\",\"label\":\"Overall launch ready\",\"ready\":false,\"severity\":\"warning\",\"detail\":\"All launch gates are green.\",\"action\":\"Address failed gates before launch.\"},{\"id\":\"realtime-circuit-state\",\"label\":\"Realtime circuit state\",\"ready\":true,\"severity\":\"info\",\"detail\":\"Current circuit state: CLOSED\",\"action\":\"Use chaos reset or fix gateway failures if the circuit remains open.\"}],\"id\":\"checklist-1775969755585\",\"recordType\":\"checklist_snapshot\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-12 12:55:55\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-12 12:55:55\"},\"recommendedActions\":[\"Sync baseline unavailable: 读取 ES alias 失败: product_search_read\",\"Latest regression run is stale.\",\"Prepare at least one usable rollback candidate index.\",\"Run or refresh a passing load test record before launch.\",\"Generate a fresh passing launch checklist snapshot.\"]},\"documents\":{\"opsRunbook\":{\"title\":\"运维手册\",\"path\":\"launch/ops-runbook.md\",\"content\":\"# 智能检索系统运维手册\\n\\n## 1. 启动前检查\\n- 确认 `W12 baselineReport` 无未处理 failed / dead-letter 任务\\n- 确认 `W13 release preflight` 通过，且 regression run 未过期\\n- 确认 `W14 final-summary` 中 `finalReady=true`\\n- 确认 Elasticsearch、MySQL、Python Query Parser、Realtime Gateway 可达\\n\\n## 2. 日常巡检\\n- 查看治理台总览和上线准备中心\\n- 检查 realtime circuit 是否意外打开\\n- 检查 metrics daily / error attribution trend 是否出现异常抬升\\n- 检查最近 release record 的 verification / governance summary\\n\\n## 3. 异常处置优先级\\n1. 用户主链不可用：先切回保守回答或 fallback\\n2. 实时链路异常：先执行 circuit reset / smoke，再决定是否切 fallback\\n3. 索引异常：优先校验 alias，再决定 rebuild 或 rollback\\n4. 评估回归失败：停止发布流转，回退到最近稳定 release\\n\\n## 4. 管理端必用入口\\n- `/admin/governance/dashboard`\\n- `/admin/governance/release`\\n- `/admin/launch/center`\\n\\n## 5. 发布前动作\\n- 执行固定版本 regression\\n- 执行 smoke\\n- 记录 load test\\n- 记录故障演练\\n- 生成 checklist snapshot\\n- 查看 final summary\\n\"},\"rollbackPlaybook\":{\"title\":\"回滚预案\",\"path\":\"launch/rollback-playbook.md\",\"content\":\"# 智能检索系统回滚预案\\n\\n## 1. 触发条件\\n- 发布后关键指标显著恶化\\n- 评估回放出现高风险 regression\\n- realtime gateway 大面积失败且 fallback 无法接受\\n- 搜索索引 alias 指向异常或结果错误率明显上升\\n\\n## 2. 回滚顺序\\n1. 停止 release record 继续流转\\n2. 固定当前故障窗口的 replay / metrics / error attribution\\n3. 若问题在索引层：\\n   - 查看 `products/index/rollback/candidates`\\n   - 执行自动回滚或手动切换 alias\\n4. 若问题在灰度策略：\\n   - 移除 gray config\\n   - 将 release record 回退到 `ready` 或 `rolled_back`\\n5. 若问题在 realtime：\\n   - 强制 fallback\\n   - 保留 smoke 结果和 circuit 状态截图\\n\\n## 3. 回滚后验证\\n- 重新执行 smoke\\n- 检查 W12 baseline 和 alias validation\\n- 检查 W13 governance summary\\n- 记录 rollback 事件与处置说明\\n\\n## 4. 必须沉淀的证据\\n- release record / release events\\n- final summary\\n- smoke 结果\\n- load test / drill 记录\\n- 关键 replay 样本\\n\"},\"goLiveChecklist\":{\"title\":\"上线清单\",\"path\":\"launch/go-live-checklist.md\",\"content\":\"# 智能检索系统上线清单\\n\\n## 基线\\n- [ ] W12 baseline report 通过\\n- [ ] alias validation 通过\\n- [ ] rollback candidate 可用\\n\\n## 治理\\n- [ ] release preflight 通过\\n- [ ] governance summary 无 blocker\\n- [ ] 最新 regression run 在新鲜度窗口内\\n\\n## 实时层\\n- [ ] realtime smoke 通过\\n- [ ] realtime circuit 为 CLOSED\\n- [ ] live gateway 已绑定\\n\\n## 演练与压测\\n- [ ] 已记录最近一次 load test\\n- [ ] 已记录最近一次故障演练\\n- [ ] final summary 为 ready\\n\\n## 收尾\\n- [ ] 运维手册已确认\\n- [ ] 回滚预案已确认\\n- [ ] 发布负责人已确认执行窗口\\n\"}}},\"gatewayConfig\":{\"gatewayMode\":\"internal\",\"internalGatewayHealth\":{\"status\":\"UP\",\"enabled\":true,\"gatewayMode\":\"internal\",\"providerSummary\":{\"providerCount\":3,\"providers\":{\"event\":{\"implemented\":false,\"entityType\":\"event\",\"reason\":\"provider_not_implemented\"},\"product\":{\"implemented\":true,\"entityType\":\"product\",\"orchestratorEnabled\":true},\"store\":{\"implemented\":false,\"entityType\":\"store\",\"reason\":\"provider_not_implemented\"}}},\"productProviderReady\":true,\"storeProviderReady\":false,\"eventProviderReady\":false},\"enabled\":true,\"gatewayEnabled\":false,\"mockGatewayEnabled\":false,\"gatewayBaseUrl\":\"http://127.0.0.1:9010\",\"gatewayQueryPath\":\"/query\",\"gatewayConnectTimeoutMs\":200,\"gatewayReadTimeoutMs\":450,\"gatewayRetryCount\":1,\"cacheTtlSeconds\":15,\"circuitFailureThreshold\":3,\"circuitOpenSeconds\":30},\"dependencyChecks\":[{\"dependencyName\":\"rabbitmq-local\",\"operator\":\"codex\",\"ready\":false,\"status\":\"blocked\",\"notes\":\"Backend log shows localhost:5672 connection refused during local startup.\",\"summary\":\"rabbitmq-local blocked by codex\",\"id\":\"dependency-1775969756022\",\"recordType\":\"dependency_check\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-12 12:55:56\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-12 12:55:56\"},{