72451654\",\"recordType\":\"dependency_check\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-12 13:40:51\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-12 13:40:51\"},\"python-sidecar\":{\"dependencyName\":\"python-sidecar\",\"operator\":\"codex\",\"ready\":true,\"status\":\"ready\",\"notes\":\"127.0.0.1:9001 reachable during post-fix verification.\",\"summary\":\"python-sidecar checked by codex\",\"id\":\"dependency-1775972451795\",\"recordType\":\"dependency_check\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-12 13:40:51\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-12 13:40:51\"},\"internal-realtime-gateway\":{\"dependencyName\":\"internal-realtime-gateway\",\"operator\":\"codex\",\"ready\":true,\"status\":\"ready\",\"notes\":\"Gateway mode internal, gatewayEnabled=True, mockGatewayEnabled=True, launchPathReady=True.\",\"summary\":\"internal-realtime-gateway checked by codex\",\"id\":\"dependency-1775972451930\",\"recordType\":\"dependency_check\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-12 13:40:51\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-12 13:40:51\"}}},\"activeLaunchWindow\":{\"windowName\":\"w14-local-go-live-20260412-r2\",\"operator\":\"codex\",\"startAt\":\"2026-04-12 13:40:50\",\"endAt\":\"\",\"status\":\"open\",\"notes\":\"Local W14 launch window opened after full repair and rehearsal refresh.\",\"summary\":\"Launch window opened by codex\",\"id\":\"window-1775972450862\",\"recordType\":\"launch_window\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-12 13:40:50\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-12 13:40:50\"},\"gatewayConfig\":{\"gatewayMode\":\"internal\",\"internalGatewayHealth\":{\"status\":\"UP\",\"enabled\":true,\"gatewayMode\":\"internal\",\"providerSummary\":{\"providerCount\":3,\"providers\":{\"event\":{\"implemented\":false,\"entityType\":\"event\",\"reason\":\"provider_not_implemented\"},\"product\":{\"implemented\":true,\"entityType\":\"product\",\"orchestratorEnabled\":true},\"store\":{\"implemented\":false,\"entityType\":\"store\",\"reason\":\"provider_not_implemented\"}}},\"productProviderReady\":true,\"storeProviderReady\":false,\"eventProviderReady\":false},\"enabled\":true,\"gatewayEnabled\":true,\"mockGatewayEnabled\":true,\"gatewayBaseUrl\":\"http://127.0.0.1:9010\",\"gatewayQueryPath\":\"/query\",\"gatewayConnectTimeoutMs\":200,\"gatewayReadTimeoutMs\":450,\"gatewayRetryCount\":1,\"cacheTtlSeconds\":15,\"circuitFailureThreshold\":3,\"circuitOpenSeconds\":30},\"documents\":{\"opsRunbook\":{\"title\":\"运维手册\",\"path\":\"launch/ops-runbook.md\",\"content\":\"# 智能检索系统运维手册\\n\\n## 1. 启动前检查\\n- 确认 `W12 baselineReport` 无未处理 failed / dead-letter 任务\\n- 确认 `W13 release preflight` 通过，且 regression run 未过期\\n- 确认 `W14 final-summary` 中 `finalReady=true`\\n- 确认 Elasticsearch、MySQL、Python Query Parser、Realtime Gateway 可达\\n\\n## 2. 日常巡检\\n- 查看治理台总览和上线准备中心\\n- 检查 realtime circuit 是否意外打开\\n- 检查 metrics daily / error attribution trend 是否出现异常抬升\\n- 检查最近 release record 的 verification / governance summary\\n\\n## 3. 异常处置优先级\\n1. 用户主链不可用：先切回保守回答或 fallback\\n2. 实时链路异常：先执行 circuit reset / smoke，再决定是否切 fallback\\n3. 索引异常：优先校验 alias，再决定 rebuild 或 rollback\\n4. 评估回归失败：停止发布流转，回退到最近稳定 release\\n\\n## 4. 管理端必用入口\\n- `/admin/governance/dashboard`\\n- `/admin/governance/release`\\n- `/admin/launch/center`\\n\\n## 5. 发布前动作\\n- 执行固定版本 regression\\n- 执行 smoke\\n- 记录 load test\\n- 记录故障演练\\n- 生成 checklist snapshot\\n- 查看 final summary\\n\"},\"rollbackPlaybook\":{\"title\":\"回滚预案\",\"path\":\"launch/rollback-playbook.md\",\"content\":\"# 智能检索系统回滚预案\\n\\n## 1. 触发条件\\n- 发布后关键指标显著恶化\\n- 评估回放出现高风险 regression\\n- realtime gateway 大面积失败且 fallback 无法接受\\n- 搜索索引 alias 指向异常或结果错误率明显上升\\n\\n## 2. 回滚顺序\\n1. 停止 release record 继续流转\\n2. 固定当前故障窗口的 replay / metrics / error attribution\\n3. 若问题在索引层：\\n   - 查看 `products/index/rollback/candidates`\\n   - 执行自动回滚或手动切换 alias\\n4. 若问题在灰度策略：\\n   - 移除 gray config\\n   - 将 release record 回退到 `ready` 或 `rolled_back`\\n5. 若问题在 realtime：\\n   - 强制 fallback\\n   - 保留 smoke 结果和 circuit 状态截图\\n\\n## 3. 回滚后验证\\n- 重新执行 smoke\\n- 检查 W12 baseline 和 alias validation\\n- 检查 W13 governance summary\\n- 记录 rollback 事件与处置说明\\n\\n## 4. 必须沉淀的证据\\n- release record / release events\\n- final summary\\n- smoke 结果\\n- load test / drill 记录\\n- 关键 replay 样本\\n\"},\"goLiveChecklist\":{\"title\":\"上线清单\",\"path\":\"launch/go-live-checklist.md\",\"content\":\"# 智能检索系统上线清单\\n\\n## 基线\\n- [ ] W12 baseline report 通过\\n- [ ] alias validation 通过\\n- [ ] rollback candidate 可用\\n\\n## 治理\\n- [ ] release preflight 通过\\n- [ ] governance summary 无 blocker\\n- [ ] 最新 regression run 在新鲜度窗口内\\n\\n## 实时层\\n- [ ] realtime smoke 通过\\n- [ ] realtime circuit 为 CLOSED\\n- [ ] live gateway 已绑定\\n\\n## 演练与压测\\n- [ ] 已记录最近一次 load test\\n- [ ] 已记录最近一次故障演练\\n- [ ] final summary 为 ready\\n\\n## 收尾\\n- [ ] 运维手册已确认\\n- [ ] 回滚预案已确认\\n- [ ] 发布负责人已确认执行窗口\\n\"}},\"summary\":{\"generatedAt\":\"2026-04-12 13:40:52\",\"finalReady\":true,\"gates\":{\"readinessGate\":true,\"loadTestReady\":true,\"drillReady\":true,\"checklistReady\":true,\"finalReady\":true},\"freshnessHours\":{\"loadTest\":72,\"drill\":72,\"checklist\":24},\"readiness\":{\"stage\":\"W14\",\"generatedAt\":\"2026-04-12 13:40:52\",\"overallReady\":true,\"gates\":{\"syncReady\":true,\"governanceReady\":true,\"realtimeServiceReady\":true,\"realtimeLiveGatewayReady\":true,\"rollbackReady\":true,\"overallReady\":true},\"sync\":{\"baseline\":{\"generatedAt\":\"2026-04-12T13:40:52.763\",\"products\":{\"sourceCount\":52,\"snapshotCount\":52,\"searchableSnapshotCount\":44,\"missingSnapshotIds\":[],\"staleSnapshotIds\":[],\"indexValidation\":{\"enabled\":true,\"reachable\":true,\"versionedIndex\":\"product_search_v1\",\"readAlias\":\"product_search_read\",\"writeAlias\":\"product_search_write\",\"readTargets\":[\"product_search_v1\"],\"writeTargets\":[\"product_search_v1\"],\"readTarget\":\"product_search_v1\",\"writeTarget\":\"product_search_v1\",\"sameTarget\":true,\"readCount\":44,\"writeCount\":44,\"consistent\":true,\"snapshotValidation\":{\"enabled\":true,\"indexOrAlias\":\"product_search_v1\",\"snapshotCount\":44,\"indexCount\":44,\"missingSnapshotIds\":[],\"staleIndexIds\":[],\"consistent\":true}},\"consiste